column5: Wolud like to hear from anyone who has fished out of Armstrong on Fly-ins this year Larry S
Larry...Did you get my second E-mail? (fishing report?) Sent it last friday. Kevin M
Kevin, Thanks I got it Larry S
Hi Larry I posted a report shortly after we got back. Did you see it?
Mr. Walleye couldn't find your 2006 report from Blackbirch,but talked to you when you came out at Mattice's dock.Do you happen to know how your friend jigman2003 did this year? Larry S

Going to be heading up to Shouldice in late August...will post results upon return. BTW, when speaking with Ryan and Kathy Brady of Northern Outposts, they indicated that as of next year they will be taking over Trophy Fish Outposts' Keezhik lake camp. Been to Keezhik 8 or 9 times and am probably going to try to book something there for next year.
Hi Larry Jigman had a good trip to Ogoki with Mattice. He said they donated a ton of jigs in the wood, but that's where the walleyes were. He may be going with my group next year to Blackbirch. JL
